snippet.title: Arena Breakout - Official Season 4 'Into The Fog of War' Cinematic Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Arena Breakout is a mobile tactical first-person shooter developed by Morefun Studios. Season 4 has arrived to Arena Breakout titled 'Into The Fog of War' focusing on the tensions between Blackgold and Gresk reaching an all-time high. Take a look at the cinematic launch trailer for season 4 offering new maps, weapons, modes, and more for Arena Breakout Season 4, available now for iOS and Android.
